STACK_LONG_DESC=Built by the Lemonade SDK team. Supports ROCm, Vulkan, and Ryzen AI NPU acceleration — all three backends in a single image. Exposes OpenAI-compatible, Anthropic, and Ollama APIs on port 13305. Models are pulled automatically from HuggingFace. Works on any modern AMD GPU and on Ryzen AI APUs without discrete VRAM.
